Seq1.ReceiverContent: Good afternoon. Thank you for calling Crofton Family Practice. This is Dominic. I'll be assisting you for the day.

Seq2.CallerContent: Hi. Can I talk to the front desk, please?
Seq2.ReceiverContent: Sure, ma'am. Kindly give me a minute. Let me transfer the call. Have a great day.

Seq3.ReceiverContent: Hello. You have reached the receptionist at Crofton Family Practice. Please leave your name, reason for calling, and your number so we can call you back as soon as we can.

Seq4.ReceiverContent: If you are experiencing a medical emergency, please hang up and dial 911. If you are calling after hours or on weekends, we have an answering service that you can call.

Seq5.ReceiverContent: If you think this is an urgent matter that the physician needs to address, you can call that answering service number at 443-481-1000. Thanks for calling.

Seq6.CallerContent: Hi. This is Catherine Gillis at 443-375-8416. My husband, James Gillis, his birthday is 7549, has an appointment, a telepathy, and he's going to be at Crofton Family Practice.
Seq6.ReceiverContent: He will visit on Thursday, and I'm going to cancel that. We're going to make a decision to go to the urgent care. I feel like he needs to be seen before Thursday.

Seq7.CallerContent: So thanks anyway, and again, my number is 443-375-8416. Thank you.
